<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Darnel" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Darnel,</orth> the plant Lolium temulentum: <bibl n="shak. h5 5.2.45" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 V, 2, 45</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 4.4.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. IV, 4, 5</bibl>. Thought to be injurious to the eyes: <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.2.44" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A III, 2, 44</bibl>.
